title: BigFish Games - Monster Quest - Hidden Object Puzzle - Wendy99
description:
Monster Quest


Step into the role of Agent for Monster Quest, where you possess 
the skills and resources to hunt down and unravel the most puzzling 
monster-sighting cases in human history. Obscure legends? Elaborate 
hoaxes? Scour the remote reaches of the Earth, interview witnesses, 
and cross-reference your data. Could there be some truth these myths? 
Only you can bring the facts to light.

    * Remote and exotic locations
    * Investigate and analyze
    * Monsters of legend revealed!

System Requirements:
OS: Windows XP/Vista
CPU: 600 Mhz
RAM: 256 MB
DirectX: 6.0
